column6: <text>１３６</text><translation>136</translation><text>ところでなんじゃ大将猟期外に鉄砲なぞ持って</text><translation>By the way, what's with the gun outside of hunting season?</translation><text>それにワシの視覚と酵覚はちっとやそっとじゃだますことはできんぞ</text><translation>And you can't fool my eyes and ears just a little bit.</translation><text>喜獣駆除です</text><translation>It's for pest control.</translation><text>本気で襲われてたまるか</text><translation>I won't let them attack me seriously.</translation><text>ククッ</text><translation>Kukuku</translation><text>ばかにしなさんな特にワシはどんなに時がたとうが忘れはせんよ</text><translation>Don't underestimate me, especially since I won't forget no matter how much time passes.</translation><text>そりゃ天然記念物のイヌワシを撃ったのだからたいへんなのはわかってるけど</text><translation>Well, I know it's serious because I shot a protected bird.</translation><text>何十年たとうとな</text><translation>No matter how many decades pass</translation><text>！</text><translation>!</translation><text>ハハハ本気で襲ったりせんよ安心しなされ</text><translation>Hahaha, don't worry, I'm not going to attack you seriously.</translation><text>じょうだんじゃない</text><translation>I'm not joking.</translation><text>馬なんかが覚えているはずないでしょ</text><translation>A horse wouldn't remember something like that, right?</translation><text>視野外でも声だけで十分それがだれだか確認できるぞ</text><translation>Even if it's out of sight, I can confirm who it is just by hearing their voice.</translation><text>たくさんの人の中であろうが扮装しようが判別できる</text><translation>Whether there are many people or they're in disguise, I can tell who they are.</translation><text>なぁにあんたに鉄砲で撃たれたのを覚えとるんじゃ</text><translation>What? You still remember being shot by me with a gun?</translation><text>わぁまた！４か月も前のことを</text><translation>Wow again! You remember something that happened four months ago!</translation>
column7: わぁまた！４か月も前のことを

Oh no!</translation><text>ズ．．</text><translation>Zzz...</translation><text>行って来ます！</text><translation>I'm going out!</translation><text>まったく口が悪いんだから</text><translation>You really have a bad mouth</translation><text>！</text><translation>!</translation><text>どうですいっしょに</text><translation>How about coming with me?</translation><text>わしはもう猟師じゃないよ</text><translation>I'm not a hunter anymore</translation><text>うん</text><translation>Yeah</translation><text>あの古ギツネめ</text><translation>That old fox</translation><text>射殺許可が出たからにはもう好き勝手はさせませんよ</text><translation>Now that the shooting permit has been issued, I won't let you do as you please</translation><text>ん傷はすっかりいいのじゃが．．．でも当分だめじゃ</text><translation>My wound is completely healed... but I can't do anything for a while</translation><text>ユキも山へ帰るんじゃよ</text><translation>Yuki is also going back to the mountains</translation><text>もう十分離せるでしょ</text><translation>It's already far enough away, right?</translation><text>あんたが山へ入るとなるとまた撃たれちゃたまらん</text><translation>If you go into the mountains, you'll get shot again</translation><text>さんざん殺生をやったわしがいうのは虫がいいようじゃが</text><translation>Even though I've done so much killing, it feels good to say this</translation><text>もう殺生はせんみんな山神様の使いじゃからのう</text><translation>I won't kill anymore, everyone is a messenger of the mountain god</translation><text>保護の立場へまわろうと思うとる</text><translation>I want to change my position to protection</translation>

text_translated: 世の中虎穴に入らずんば虎子を得ずだ
column6: <text>世の中虎穴に入らずんば虎子を得ずだ</text><translation>You won't get tiger cubs unless you enter the tiger's den.</translation><text>旅行してぇだけだろ！！</text><translation>You just want to go on a trip, right!!</translation><text>先生はそれをお前に教えたい</text><translation>The teacher wants to teach you that.</translation><text>お前が石橋を叩いて渡るのが好きなのはわかるが</text><translation>I understand that you like to cross the river by tapping the stones, but</translation><text>だから先生が温泉に行ってる間天文部を頼む</text><translation>So I'm counting on you to take care of the astronomy club while the teacher is at the hot spring.</translation><text>～</text><translation>~</translation><text>１</text><translation>1</translation><text>まあ聞け</text><translation>Well, listen.</translation><text>！？</text><translation>!?</translation><text>ちょっ</text><translation>Huh</translation><text>なんで関係ない部活の手伝いなんかー</text><translation>Why do I have to help with some unrelated club activity-</translation><text>！</text><translation>!</translation><text>．．．</text><translation>...</translation><text>お前には夏休みの間</text><translation>During the summer break,</translation><text>我が天文部の手伝いをしてもらう</text><translation>I'll have you help out with my astronomy club.</translation>
